<div class="section_title">Exhibitor-Appointed Contractors: Online Registration Deadline</div>
<span class="text">
Designate your Exhibitor-Appointed Contractors (EAC) with the new online registration tool. <BR><BR>Appoint your EAC online at <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/myEAC">www.CESweb.org/myEAC</A>, and your EAC&nbsp;can sign off on their EAC agreement, submit the certificate of insurance and order worker wristbands. <BR><BR>The deadline was December 3, 2004. If you don’t appoint your EAC now, they will not be able to get on the show floor.
</span>
<a name="2160"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Space Selection Packs </div>
<span class="text">
If you plan to exhibit in the 2006 International CES, you’ll want to keep an eye out for the Exhibit Space Selection Mailing, coming in early December.
<P>The 2006 International CES Exhibit Space Selection reminder will contain all you need to know about choosing your space for next year’s show. Keep an eye out for it!</P>Questions? Contact <A href="mailto:sdevore@ce.org">Sylvia DeVore</A>.
</span>
<a name="2159"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Have You Registered Your Booth Staff?</div>
<span class="text">
If you register your booth personnel this week, you might still receive your staff badges in the mail. 
<P><A href="/exhibitors/resource_center/badges/default.asp">Register your booth staff&nbsp;by December 3, 2004</A> to receive your badges in the mail. We’ve made it easy for you to register large groups: Simply upload a spreadsheet with the information for all of your booth personnel. </P>Questions? Please contact the International CES Customer Service at <A href="mailto:CESinfo@CE.org">CESinfo@CE.org</A> or (866) 233-7968. (Outside the U.S., call 011-301-631-3983.)
</span>
<a name="2158"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">What Are You Doing to Steal the Stage?</div>
<span class="text">
You only have one shot. Get ready to grab the spotlight with CES <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/default.asp">promotional opportunities</A>, and pack the power of building your brand at the International CES.
<P>Let us help you plan the best ways to get your company, brand and products noticed.&nbsp; </P>
<P><STRONG>Pre-show Promotion</STRONG><BR>Communicate your corporate message to an audience of attendees eager to attend CES. Whether your strategy includes <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/mail.asp#681">e-marketing</A>&nbsp;or <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/mail.asp#683">direct mail to CES attendees</A>, we’ll help you reach the attendees you want to target.</P>
<P><STRONG>On-site Opportunities</STRONG><BR>Reach qualified press and analysts early: Sponsor the <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/press.asp#671">Press/Analysts Breakfasts</A>, so you can make sure to get your logo in front of them.</P>
<P>Put your logo on the <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/sponsorships.asp#2077">Interactive Floor Plan/Product Locator Kiosks</A>, used by attendees planning a strategy to see specific exhibitors and products. </P>
<P><IMG height=64 hspace=6 src="/images/general/channelintelligence.gif" width=135 align=right border=0 target="_blank">Join leaders like the <A href="/exhibitors/space/suites.asp">CES Meeting Place</A>&nbsp;sponsor, Channel Intelligence, the company providing commerce data interchange services among manufacturers and dealers.</P>For more details, contact Wendy Hudak at (703) 907-7688 or <A href="mailto:byb@CE.org">byb@CE.org</A>
</span>
<a name="2157"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Innovations Plus in CES Central Plaza</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG hspace=6 src="/images/general/innovationplus160.gif" align=right>There’s a new home for the hottest new technologies in the CE industry, so put Innovations Plus on your <EM>must-see list</EM>.
<P><A href="/attendees/show_floor/areas/central_plaza.asp">Innovations Plus</A> includes the award-winning Innovations Design and Engineering Showcase Honorees, more than 100 breakthrough technology exhibitors and the largest concentration of specialized TechZones at CES and more. </P>Don’t miss it!
</span>
<a name="2156"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Automotive Aftermarket Showcase Arrives</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=27 hspace=6 src="/images/general/techzone_small.gif" width=120 align=right>Mobile technologies are shifting into high gear at CES. For the first time ever, the International CES will feature the Automotive Aftermarket Showcase.
<P>The International CES is the largest mobile technologies tradeshow in the world. Forty thousand decision makers—one in three attendees—come to see and buy mobile electronics.</P>Make sure you check out the competition in the <A href="/attendees/show_floor/techzones/default.asp#525">Automotive Aftermarket Showcase</A>, LVCC North Hall.
</span>
<a name="2155"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Parking at the Alexis Park</div>
<span class="text">
Complimentary parking at the Alexis Park for the 2005 International CES will be limited. 
<P>Parking on-site will open up in designated areas on show days starting on Thursday, January 6 through Saturday, January 8 at 6 p.m. Vehicles remaining in designated areas after 6 p.m. on January 8 will be towed to an alternate location. In addition, supplemental complimentary parking will also be available January 4-10 and is accessible from the front of the Alexis Park.</P>Exhibitors checking into the hotel will be given a parking pass at the front desk.
</span>
<a name="2154"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<img src="/global_images2005/2.0.line.gif" alt="-----------------------------------------------" width="100%" height="2" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

<div class="section_title">Introducing the Demmy Awards for Quality Audio</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG hspace=6 src="/images/general/demmy.gif" align=right>Get ready to nominate the best examples of audio available to consumers.
<P>The <A href="/attendees/awards/demmy.asp">Demmy Awards</A>, sponsored by the Consumer Electronics Association (CEA), producer of the International CES, is for audio-video professionals who use sound demonstrations to help consumers invest in the best possible choice of audio equipment. </P>
<P>From DVDs to CDs to music videos, you’ll be able to nominate your choice for the audio materials with the biggest <EM>'Wow factor.'</EM> </P>CEA will accept nominations for this new awards program at the 2005 International CES and online at <A href="http://www.ce.org/DemmyAwards" target=_blank>http://www.CE.org/DemmyAwards</A>. Look for the DEMMY Awards signs at select exhibits at the <A href="/attendees/show_floor/areas/alexis_park.asp">Alexis Park</A>.
</span>
<a name="2177"></a>
<img src="/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

