<div class="section_title">Outdoor Advertising</div>
<span class="text">
Make a colossal statement. Reach the masses. Reserve <A href="/exhibitors/promotions/onsite.asp">on-site advertising opportunities today</A>.
<P>CES offers unparalleled opportunities to connect you with your target audience. There's still time to reserve outdoor advertising at the LVCC, <EM>but you must act fast</EM>.&nbsp; </P>
<P>New locations for banners and kiosks are available in areas that will get the kind of attention and recall to boost your presence at CES! </P>Call Liz Tardif at (401) 849-9300, or e-mail <A href="mailto:ltardif@CE.org">ltardif@CE.org</A> for an updated list of opportunities.
</span>
